# Responses to a major suit opening

# C = ♣
# D = ♦
# H = ♥
# S = ♠

2♣ 2M => 5+ M, 8+ tpts, 2 of top 3 in M;
    test AQxxx Kxx xxx xx:
        2♣ 2S;
2♣ 3m => 5+ m, 8+ tpts, 2 of top 3 in m;
    test xx Kxx AQxxx xxx:
        2♣ 3D;

2♣ 2N => 8+ tpts, balanced, partial_stoppers unbid;
    test Qx Kxxx Kxxx Jxx:
        2♣ 2N;

2♣ 2D => always;
    test xx Kxxx xxxx xxx:
        2♣ 2D;

2♣ 2D
2N => balanced, 22-24 tpts, 22-24 hcp;
    test AKQx AQxx AQ Qxx:
        2C 2D
        2N;
